dcterms:description: The Pleophylla dataset consists of images of female genitalia from 112 specimens across 7 species of the South African genus Pleophylla, characterized by low differentiation among species and challenging identification conditions.
dcterms:title: Pleophylla Dataset

dcterms:description: The Schizonycha dataset includes images of male copulation organs from 76 specimens across 33 species of the African genus Schizonycha, with a focus on identifying species despite imbalanced sample distribution.
dcterms:title: Schizonycha Dataset
